<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 22:04:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>关于哈马斯激进组织对以色列前所未有的袭击，你需要了解的 5 件事</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/5-things-to-know-about-the-hamas-militant-groups-unprecedented-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104247664.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247664.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙哈马斯统治者对以色列发动多管齐下的进攻，令该国措手不及。这次袭击包括火箭弹，炸毁了以色列部分强化隔离栅栏，并渗透到加沙边境沿线的以色列社区。哈马斯声称俘虏了以色列士兵，并发布了视频，显示武装分子拖着血迹斑斑的士兵并站在尸体旁。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 21:39:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/5-things-to-know-about-the-hamas-militant-groups-unprecedented-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104247664.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国和法国加强犹太场所的安全</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-france-step-up-security-at-jewish-sites/articleshow/104247550.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247550.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯对以色列发动突然袭击后，德国和法国周六采取行动，加强犹太寺庙、学校和纪念碑周围的安全。法国将重点放在全国各地城市的犹太寺庙和学校上，一位犹太领导人对冲突可能蔓延到那里的可能性表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 21:30:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-france-step-up-security-at-jewish-sites/articleshow/104247550.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普周六访问爱荷华州，试图巩固他在该州的支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-sets-his-sights-on-iowa-with-visits-saturday-as-he-tries-to-solidify-his-support-in-the-state/articleshow/104247506.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247506.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着 2024 年共和党提名的临近，前总统唐纳德·特朗普正在爱荷华州加紧竞选努力。特朗普在滑铁卢和锡达拉皮兹举行了活动，吸引了大量人群，并强调赢得党团会议的重要性。他指责乔·拜登总统对哈马斯袭击以色列负责，并再次攻击纽约总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯，后者正在对他提起民事欺诈案。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 21:03:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-sets-his-sights-on-iowa-with-visits-saturday-as-he-tries-to-solidify-his-support-in-the-state/articleshow/104247506.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯敦促巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯恢复约旦河西岸的平静与稳定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blinken-urges-palestinian-president-abbas-to-restore-calm-stability-in-west-bank/articleshow/104247412.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247412.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务院在一份声明中表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周六在与巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯的通话中敦促巴勒斯坦权力机构恢复约旦河西岸的平静与稳定。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 20:26:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blinken-urges-palestinian-president-abbas-to-restore-calm-stability-in-west-bank/articleshow/104247412.cms</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：以色列军队将“使用一切武力摧毁哈马斯”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-army-to-use-all-force-to-destroy-hamas-netanyahu/articleshow/104247367.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247367.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;内塔尼亚胡在一份简短的电视声明中表示：“以色列国防军将动用全部力量摧毁哈马斯的能力。”“我们将打击他们到底，并在他们给以色列带来的黑暗日子里用武力报仇。”及其人民，”在哈马斯武装分子黎明发动突袭后，他说道。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 20:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-army-to-use-all-force-to-destroy-hamas-netanyahu/articleshow/104247367.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登誓言“坚如磐石”地支持以色列和国防支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-vows-rock-solid-support-for-israel-defense-support/articleshow/104246756.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104246756.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国谴责哈马斯恐怖分子对以色列的袭击，并承诺支持以色列的防御。乔·拜登总统表达了对以色列的声援，并强调美国坚定支持以色列的安全。国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀重申了确保以色列拥有必要资源的承诺。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 18:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-vows-rock-solid-support-for-israel-defense-support/articleshow/104246756.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击以色列后联合国安理会将就中东局势举行闭门会议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unsc-to-hold-close-door-session-on-middle-east-situation-after-hamas-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104247286.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247286.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周六，中东发生重大剧变，哈马斯恐怖组织发动“突然袭击”，向以色列南部和中部发射火箭弹。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 19:44:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unsc-to-hold-close-door-session-on-middle-east-situation-after-hamas-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104247286.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿巴斯告诉布林肯，对巴勒斯坦人的不公正导致冲突“爆炸”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/abbas-tells-blinken-injustice-towards-palestinians-driving-conflict-to-explosion/articleshow/104247180.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247180.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据WAFA报道，阿巴斯在电话中还表示，持续升级的原因是“殖民主义者和以色列占领军的做法，以及对伊斯兰教和基督教神圣地位的侵犯”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 19:20:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/abbas-tells-blinken-injustice-towards-palestinians-driving-conflict-to-explosion/articleshow/104247180.cms</guid></item><item><title>约旦和欧盟讨论采取国际行动阻止加沙局势升级的必要性</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/jordan-eu-discuss-need-for-international-action-to-stop-gaza-escalation/articleshow/104247130.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247130.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;约旦外交部周六在一份声明中表示，约旦外交部长艾曼·萨法迪在与欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔的电话中讨论了采取国际行动阻止加沙局势升级的必要性。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 19:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/jordan-eu-discuss-need-for-international-action-to-stop-gaza-escalation/articleshow/104247130.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国将永远支持以色列——拜登</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-will-always-have-israels-back-biden/articleshow/104247085.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104247085.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; “我们永远不会让她回来，”拜登在白宫与国务卿安东尼·布林肯站在一起说道。拜登补充说：“现在不是任何敌视以色列的政党利用这些袭击的时候。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 19:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-will-always-have-israels-back-biden/articleshow/104247085.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发动突然袭击后，以色列和加沙陷入战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-gaza-at-war-after-hamas-launches-surprise-attack/articleshow/104246742.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104246742.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯周六对以色列发动大规模突然袭击，从加沙发射了数千枚火箭弹，并派出地面部队杀害或绑架人员，而以色列则以空袭进行报复。以色列当局称，以色列境内有10人被火箭弹袭击身亡，30人被枪击身亡。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 18:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-gaza-at-war-after-hamas-launches-surprise-attack/articleshow/104246742.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其准备帮助缓和巴以冲突</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-ready-to-help-de-escalate-israeli-palestinian-conflict/articleshow/104246676.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104246676.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;土耳其外交部长哈坎·菲丹与沙特阿拉伯、卡塔尔、伊朗、巴勒斯坦和埃及等地区同行进行了讨论，以解决以色列和巴勒斯坦之间持续的冲突。土耳其表示愿意帮助缓和局势，并谴责平民的生命损失。该国的目标是防止冲突进一步升级，并确保冲突得到控制，不会蔓延到更广泛的地区。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 18:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-ready-to-help-de-escalate-israeli-palestinian-conflict/articleshow/104246676.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京盟友建议推迟三月总统选举，或排除竞争对手</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-suggests-postponing-march-presidential-election-or-excluding-rivals/articleshow/104245150.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104245150.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯车臣地区负责人、总统弗拉基米尔·普京的亲密盟友拉姆赞·卡德罗夫周六提议，原定于明年三月举行的总统选举要么因乌克兰战争而推迟，要么仅限于一名候选人——普京。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 15:46:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-ally-suggests-postponing-march-presidential-election-or-excluding-rivals/articleshow/104245150.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦政府宣布驱逐非法移民，卡拉奇的阿富汗人陷入恐惧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/fear-grips-afghans-in-karachi-as-pakistan-government-announces-evicting-illegal-immigrants/articleshow/104244710.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104244710.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 15:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/fear-grips-afghans-in-karachi-as-pakistan-government-announces-evicting-illegal-immigrants/articleshow/104244710.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯对以色列的意外袭击危及地区地缘政治</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/surprise-hamas-attack-on-israel-imperils-regional-geopolitics/articleshow/104244366.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104244366.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 14:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/surprise-hamas-attack-on-israel-imperils-regional-geopolitics/articleshow/104244366.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登被指控没有针对沙特阿拉伯采取行动，从而在卡舒吉民意调查中出尔反尔</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-accused-of-backtracking-on-his-khashoggi-poll-plank-by-not-acting-against-saudi-arabia/articleshow/104246492.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104246492.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;人权活动人士和一些民主党人指责美国总统乔·拜登背弃了重新评估与沙特阿拉伯关系的承诺。他们声称拜登正在寻求改善与沙特阿拉伯的关系，以对抗中国的扩张并维持美国在中东的霸权。批评者认为这是对贾迈勒·卡舒吉和美国人民的背叛。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 17:58:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-accused-of-backtracking-on-his-khashoggi-poll-plank-by-not-acting-against-saudi-arabia/articleshow/104246492.cms</guid></item><item><title>泽连斯基称以色列拥有“无可争议”的防御权</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/zelenskyy-says-israel-has-indisputable-right-to-defence/articleshow/104243909.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104243909.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;正在抵御俄罗斯入侵的乌克兰总统泽连斯基周六表示，以色列毫无疑问有权防御巴勒斯坦武装分子的袭击。乌克兰外交部早些时候表示，“强烈谴责针对以色列的持续恐怖袭击，包括针对耶路撒冷和特拉维夫平民的火箭袭击”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 14:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/zelenskyy-says-israel-has-indisputable-right-to-defence/articleshow/104243909.cms</guid></item><item><title>移民委内瑞拉人并未因美国计划恢复驱逐航班而却步</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/migrating-venezuelans-undeterred-by-us-plan-to-resume-deportation-flights/articleshow/104243650.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104243650.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周五，在巴拿马达里恩丛林边缘，委内瑞拉人占大多数移民等待巴士穿越该国前往哥斯达黎加，他们计划在那里继续向北移动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 14:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/migrating-venezuelans-undeterred-by-us-plan-to-resume-deportation-flights/articleshow/104243650.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国学校对学生的“厕所通行证”规定引发愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-schools-toilet-pass-rule-for-students-sparks-anger/articleshow/104241211.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104241211.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国一所中学要求学生出示“厕所通行证”才能在校园内使用卫生间的规定引发了不同的反应。这张盖有学校公章的通行证在社交媒体上疯传。学校声称实施这一规定是为了防止学生逃课，但遭到批评侵犯学生隐私。该规定已被废除，但当地教育部门正在调查此事。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 12:02:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-schools-toilet-pass-rule-for-students-sparks-anger/articleshow/104241211.cms</guid></item><item><title>前美国陆军情报官员因与中国分享“机密”信息而被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/ex-us-army-intelligence-officer-arrested-for-sharing-classified-information-with-china/articleshow/104241136.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104241136.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前美国陆军情报官员约瑟夫·丹尼尔·施密特因涉嫌在新冠病毒大流行期间试图向中国安全部门提供机密国防信息而被捕。施密特从香港抵达后在旧金山国际机场被捕。他自 2020 年 3 月起一直居住在香港。施密特被指控保留和试图传递国防信息。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 11:54:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/ex-us-army-intelligence-officer-arrested-for-sharing-classified-information-with-china/articleshow/104241136.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>